1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 22=

4
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:19,879
H-Heaven's Gate Shines Upon the World...

5
00:00:27,079 --> 00:00:28,960
No... Impossible!

6
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:33,679
Myriad Blades Return to the Source!

7
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:57,960
Xiaojiu...

8
00:01:01,159 --> 00:01:02,280
I have

9
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,760
avenged you.

10
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:15,719
Stop looking.

11
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:19,000
I've already searched everywhere.

12
00:01:19,879 --> 00:01:21,519
The only way out
is the pool beneath the miasma.

13
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:26,599
But jumping in is certain death.

14
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:34,959
I've been a legend all my life,

15
00:01:35,079 --> 00:01:37,200
only to die
beside a pretty boy like you.

16
00:01:38,359 --> 00:01:40,519
Heaven really
has a twisted sense of humor.

17
00:01:41,079 --> 00:01:41,879
Xiao Ziting,

18
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,159
a dying man's words

19
00:01:44,159 --> 00:01:45,079
should be honest.

20
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,159
There's something I've never understood.

21
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,319
I want a straight answer.

22
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,159
Go ahead.

23
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:54,280
Why have you always
been so hostile toward me?

24
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,319
Is it really because

25
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:59,000
I've topped the Young Hero
Heartthrob List for three years,

26
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,959
while you're always stuck at number two?

27
00:02:00,959 --> 00:02:01,760
Nonsense.

28
00:02:02,599 --> 00:02:03,400
Tang Feng,

29
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,599
you really underestimate me.

30
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,280
I've never cared

31
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:09,159
about that stupid ranking.

32
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,000
Then why?

33
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:13,800
You really don't remember?

34
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:15,800
Then again,

35
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,199
you were too young

36
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,759
to know what happened.

37
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,000
Ten years ago,

38
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,960
my mother fell gravely ill.

39
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:25,680
My father learned that

40
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:28,159
only the Tang Clan's Qianji Elixir

41
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:29,800
could save her.

42
00:02:30,599 --> 00:02:31,400
Later, Father took us

43
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:34,759
to the Tang Clan
to beg for the medicine.

44
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:36,860
(Tang Clan)

45
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:41,620
(Young Xiao Ziting)

46
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,080
Mother!

47
00:02:44,719 --> 00:02:45,520
Mother!

48
00:02:46,719 --> 00:02:47,639
Mother!

49
00:02:48,159 --> 00:02:49,319
Mother!

50
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,719
Only later did I learn

51
00:02:59,319 --> 00:03:02,199
the Tang Clan still had one dose left.

52
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:04,599
But the heir of the Tang Clan,

53
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,560
meaning you,

54
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,560
had caught a cold
and couldn't shake a high fever.

55
00:03:08,759 --> 00:03:10,080
Desperate to save you,

56
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,800
your father lied
and said the medicine was gone,

57
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,879
then gave that last dose

58
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:15,400
to his precious son.

59
00:03:15,439 --> 00:03:16,039
You...

60
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:19,319
So that's what happened.

61
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:20,199
So you...

62
00:03:20,199 --> 00:03:21,759
So I'm just being petty
and holding a grudge.

63
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:22,199
Is that it?

64
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,360
That's not what I meant.

65
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,520
Then what did you mean?

66
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:25,879
All I know is,

67
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,800
if the Tang Clan had saved Mother,

68
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,319
she'd still be alive.

69
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:32,400
Ziting,

70
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,520
the Tang family wronged you.

71
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:35,960
On my father's behalf,

72
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:38,360
I apologize to you and your father.

73
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,400
Spare me the fake apology.

74
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,319
Use that time

75
00:03:42,319 --> 00:03:43,879
to figure out how we're getting out.

76
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,400
I don't want to die here

77
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,879
and become a wandering ghost.

78
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:54,000
There might be a way out.

79
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,960
The Corpse Miasma is drawn to blood.

80
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:57,879
If one of us uses his blood

81
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:59,400
to draw the miasma away,

82
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:02,000
the other can dive into the pool

83
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,360
and follow the current out.

84
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,400
Why didn't you say so sooner?

85
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:08,439
What are you doing?

86
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,240
What are you waiting for?

87
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:09,840
Go!

88
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,599
Are you out of your mind?

89
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:12,759
Xiao Ziting,

90
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,120
the Qianji Elixir can cure smallpox,

91
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,000
but it's highly toxic.

92
00:04:15,199 --> 00:04:15,960
Father refused

93
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,480
because your mother
was too weak to survive it.

94
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:17,839
I...

95
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:32,000
Xiao Ziting, you're insane!

96
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,879
We leave together.

97
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,399
I won't owe you one.

98
00:05:06,319 --> 00:05:06,680
Dasheng!

99
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,160
Dasheng!

100
00:05:08,879 --> 00:05:09,600
Are you all right?

101
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,600
How did you get here?

102
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,879
This isn't the place to talk.

103
00:05:13,879 --> 00:05:14,720
Let's get out of the manor first.

104
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:15,920
All right. Let's go.

105
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:32,279
You two really are lucky.

106
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:34,279
You fell into my Corpse Miasma Pool

107
00:05:34,399 --> 00:05:36,040
and still made it out alive.

108
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,319
Old monster!

109
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:38,680
That lousy Corpse Miasma Pool of yours

110
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,120
must've come straight out of you.

111
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,199
It reeks!

112
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,240
You're asking to die.

113
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,480
Go!

114
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,120
Master Baiyi is far too powerful.

115
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:56,920
You're no match for him.

116
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,839
Enough arguing.

117
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,879
If you stay, we'll all die here.

118
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,759
Bring reinforcements.

119
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:05,079
I might still make it.

120
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,800
Go!

121
00:06:13,399 --> 00:06:15,720
Peng Dasheng. You're here.

122
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,720
Old monster,

123
00:06:17,399 --> 00:06:18,680
were you

124
00:06:19,399 --> 00:06:21,079
behind Xiaojiu's death?

125
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:23,000
What if I was?

126
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:24,480
What if I wasn't?

127
00:06:25,079 --> 00:06:26,399
She was just some little brat.

128
00:06:26,399 --> 00:06:27,920
So what if she died?

129
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:29,000
Who cares

130
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,480
whether an ant lives or dies?

131
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:32,000
She was the woman I loved,

132
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,920
not an ant.

133
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:38,000
So you've come to avenge her?

134
00:06:38,199 --> 00:06:40,360
Let's find out.

135
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:52,040
A weakling born with sealed meridians

136
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:53,759
dares challenge me?

137
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:55,519
You're trying to stop the unstoppable.

138
00:06:55,519 --> 00:06:56,639
Like an ant trying to topple a tree.

139
00:06:56,639 --> 00:06:58,800
Kill me if you can.

140
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,680
Peng Dasheng, before you die,

141
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,600
don't you want to know

142
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:04,680
why I went to such lengths
to set this up?

143
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,519
Old monster,

144
00:07:06,759 --> 00:07:08,000
with your power,

145
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:10,879
it would only be a matter of time

146
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,480
before the Demon Sect
ruled the martial world.

147
00:07:14,319 --> 00:07:15,720
Your ambitions go far beyond that,

148
00:07:16,079 --> 00:07:17,800
don't they?

149
00:07:18,959 --> 00:07:20,000
Go on.

150
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,680
During the battle at Liuchu Manor,

151
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:25,399
you knew the sect leaders

152
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,000
would hold back

153
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,759
and just watch.

154
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:31,120
But you set the trap anyway.

155
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:33,160
The battle was just a diversion.

156
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:34,800
Your real target was elsewhere.

157
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,439
Then tell me,

158
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:40,560
what was my real target?

159
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:43,879
You knew I'd defeat
the Luocha Blade Demon,

160
00:07:44,399 --> 00:07:46,480
so you stayed back

161
00:07:47,399 --> 00:07:48,800
and let us wear each other down.

162
00:07:49,279 --> 00:07:50,319
The battle at Liuchu Manor
looked like a trap,

163
00:07:50,319 --> 00:07:51,600
but it was really bait.

164
00:07:51,879 --> 00:07:52,680
You only wanted

165
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,680
the major sects to lower their guard.

166
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:56,759
You didn't go to all this trouble

167
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,279
just to become
Martial Arts Alliance Leader,

168
00:07:58,279 --> 00:08:00,120
did you?

169
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:05,079
Impressive, Peng Dasheng.

170
00:08:05,199 --> 00:08:07,160
You've seen through

171
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:09,000
almost every part of my plan.

172
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:13,360
Every sect covets the title
of Martial Arts Alliance Leader.

173
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:16,199
To me, it's worthless.

174
00:08:16,959 --> 00:08:18,920
What I really want

175
00:08:19,199 --> 00:08:21,879
is to bring the entire martial world
under my rule

176
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:25,399
and become the Martial God
worshiped for all eternity.

177
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:30,399
The Martial God?

178
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,679
Old monster,

179
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:38,759
you're nothing but a murderous heretic.

180
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,200
You think you're worthy?

181
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:48,360
You mortals think the martial path

182
00:08:48,799 --> 00:08:50,360
begins and ends

183
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:52,519
in this tiny martial world.

184
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:57,600
I will bring it all under one rule.

185
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:01,000
That is my path
to becoming the Martial God.

186
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:03,399
Peng Dasheng,

187
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,519
do you know what happens

188
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:07,480
when one person gathers

189
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:10,559
the vital essence
of the world's greatest martial artists?

190
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:13,399
He can break through
the final barrier to godhood

191
00:09:13,799 --> 00:09:15,559
and live as long as heaven and earth.

192
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:18,320
So all your scheming

193
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,600
was to drain the vital essence
of every martial artist

194
00:09:22,159 --> 00:09:23,799
and transcend life and death?

195
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,879
More precisely,

196
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:30,759
they're only sacrifices
on my path to godhood.

197
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,799
Now that you know so much,

198
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:36,960
do you really think
I'll let you leave alive?

199
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:38,399
If you wanted me dead,

200
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:39,720
you'd have killed me already.

201
00:09:40,159 --> 00:09:41,720
Why wait until now?

202
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:44,759
You need me to make it out alive

203
00:09:45,399 --> 00:09:47,279
so the sect leaders will believe

204
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:49,799
the Demon Sect is no threat

205
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:52,559
if it can't even handle

206
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:54,360
a nobody like me.

207
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:57,679
What makes you so sure I won't kill you?

208
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:15,120
Peng Dasheng, even if I kill you,

209
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:18,720
the major sects will still
come to me as sacrifices.

210
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:21,519
Your life is worthless to me.

211
00:10:21,519 --> 00:10:22,600
Old monster!

212
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:25,799
You'd better kill me today.

213
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:29,759
Otherwise, I will avenge Xiaojiu.

214
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:31,600
I'd rather keep you alive

215
00:10:31,879 --> 00:10:33,720
to watch me become

216
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:36,200
supreme ruler of the martial world.

217
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:41,200
I'll wait at Busi Sea
for you to avenge her

218
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,879
I hope you're stronger by then.

219
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:46,000
Don't disappoint me.

220
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:58,799
Dasheng!

221
00:10:59,399 --> 00:11:00,200
Dasheng!

222
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,399
Dasheng!

223
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,399
Su Yeye!

224
00:11:33,279 --> 00:11:34,600
If you're here to question me,

225
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:35,960
please leave.

226
00:11:36,679 --> 00:11:37,799
I have nothing to say.

227
00:11:41,780 --> 00:11:44,220
(Martial Token)

228
00:11:44,799 --> 00:11:45,600
Ms. Su,

229
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,600
take the Martial Token
and leave the city.

230
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:48,960
No one will stop you.

231
00:11:49,679 --> 00:11:50,600
Leave while it's dark

232
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,200
and get as far away as you can.

233
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:06,919
You're really letting me go?

234
00:12:07,559 --> 00:12:08,919
I only want to know one thing.

235
00:12:10,559 --> 00:12:13,679
Who exactly is Master Baiyi?

236
00:12:22,279 --> 00:12:25,919
I've never seen his true face.

237
00:12:26,799 --> 00:12:27,679
But

238
00:12:28,519 --> 00:12:30,559
he seems to know every sect's secrets

239
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:32,000
down to the last detail.

240
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,559
In the martial world,

241
00:12:34,919 --> 00:12:35,960
the greatest threat

242
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,559
isn't the blade in front of you.

243
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:40,320
It's the enemy hiding in plain sight.

244
00:12:42,759 --> 00:12:43,759
You mean

245
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,519
he's hiding among the sects?

246
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,600
Mr. Peng,

247
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:51,759
take my advice.

248
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:54,679
Leave the martial world
while you still can.

249
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:58,000
You'll never defeat him.

250
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:01,919
Thank you for your concern, Ms. Su.

251
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,200
Now go.

252
00:13:08,100 --> 00:13:11,020
(Martial Token)

253
00:13:13,500 --> 00:13:15,620
(Martial Token)

254
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:19,000
Mr. Peng,

255
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,600
there's one more thing I want to ask.

256
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,200
After all this time,

257
00:13:27,759 --> 00:13:29,799
you still can't forget Ms. Fang?

258
00:13:34,919 --> 00:13:36,440
She's gone.

259
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:39,279
Even if I can't forget her,

260
00:13:40,759 --> 00:13:41,879
what can I do?

261
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:44,120
What if you could...

262
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,879
could see her again?

263
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,759
I don't like owing anyone.

264
00:14:13,740 --> 00:14:14,220
♪Come on♪

265
00:14:17,740 --> 00:14:19,420
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

266
00:14:21,380 --> 00:14:24,340
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

267
00:14:24,620 --> 00:14:27,540
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

268
00:14:27,780 --> 00:14:30,620
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

269
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:33,620
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

270
00:14:34,140 --> 00:14:37,100
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

271
00:14:37,340 --> 00:14:40,340
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

272
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:43,420
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

273
00:14:43,580 --> 00:14:46,340
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

274
00:14:46,900 --> 00:14:50,220
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

275
00:14:50,260 --> 00:14:53,260
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

276
00:14:53,300 --> 00:14:58,940
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

277
00:14:59,340 --> 00:15:01,380
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

278
00:15:01,940 --> 00:15:04,460
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

279
00:15:05,180 --> 00:15:07,580
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

280
00:15:07,700 --> 00:15:11,380
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

281
00:15:11,980 --> 00:15:14,100
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

282
00:15:15,020 --> 00:15:17,140
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

283
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:20,580
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

284
00:15:20,620 --> 00:15:24,900
♪I am my own king♪

285
00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:39,540
♪I emerge into the world♪

286
00:15:39,540 --> 00:15:41,300
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

287
00:15:41,300 --> 00:15:42,660
♪My pride is my trump card♪

288
00:15:42,660 --> 00:15:44,460
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

289
00:15:44,460 --> 00:15:45,860
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

290
00:15:45,860 --> 00:15:47,620
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

291
00:15:47,620 --> 00:15:49,140
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

292
00:15:49,140 --> 00:15:50,860
♪I dare to break every rule♪

293
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:52,180
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

294
00:15:52,180 --> 00:15:54,020
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

295
00:15:54,020 --> 00:15:55,260
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

296
00:15:55,260 --> 00:15:57,500
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

297
00:15:57,500 --> 00:15:59,020
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

298
00:15:59,020 --> 00:16:00,620
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

299
00:16:00,620 --> 00:16:02,220
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

300
00:16:02,220 --> 00:16:03,940
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

301
00:16:03,940 --> 00:16:05,660
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

302
00:16:05,660 --> 00:16:07,020
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

303
00:16:07,020 --> 00:16:08,660
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

304
00:16:08,660 --> 00:16:10,140
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

305
00:16:10,140 --> 00:16:11,860
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

306
00:16:11,860 --> 00:16:13,460
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

307
00:16:13,460 --> 00:16:15,020
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

308
00:16:15,020 --> 00:16:19,340
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

309
00:16:19,340 --> 00:16:21,500
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

310
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:24,100
♪Let me write the legend♪

311
00:16:28,980 --> 00:16:31,540
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

312
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:34,860
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

313
00:16:34,860 --> 00:16:37,340
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

314
00:16:37,340 --> 00:16:41,420
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

315
00:16:41,780 --> 00:16:44,380
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

316
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:46,860
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

317
00:16:46,860 --> 00:16:49,900
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

318
00:16:49,900 --> 00:16:54,940
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
